# Vision Roaster – Discord Bot with Image Understanding

## Overview
Vision Roaster is a Discord bot that takes an image as input and generates a contextual "roast" using a vision-capable AI model.

The project combines computer vision and conversational AI to create an interactive and lightweight application that works both in Discord and in a Jupyter Notebook environment.

---

## Features
- Accepts image input from Discord  
- Generates contextual responses based on visual content  
- Sends replies directly in Discord chat  
- Displays both image and response in a notebook environment  
- Uses prompt design to control tone and style of output  

---

## Tech Stack
- Python  
- Discord API  
- Vision-enabled LLM  
- Jupyter Notebook (.ipynb)  

---

## How It Works
1. User sends an image in Discord  
2. Bot captures the image and processes it  
3. Image is passed to a vision-capable model  
4. A prompt is applied to generate a roast-style response  
5. Output is sent back to Discord and optionally displayed in notebook  

---

